Sanchez: SHUT UP!!!! Pay attention to the road. Next person who looks at me, I'm gonna rip their eyeballs out!

Rune: Sanchez, thank...you...
Believer: Catch them! Quick, go tell Devious!

Sophie: Oh, no. He's going to get reinforcements!
Hanbei: There's no time! We've got to escape!
Sophie: ...Alright! Everybody, come with me!

Hutchinson: Then we'd better head——
Ru-yi: *oof*...!
Rune: Gen..eral...
Lazer: ...There's nowhere to hide. The reinforcements are already here. Looks like you've run out of luck.

Maria: Attempting to enter battle mode, attempting to enter battle mode...
Maria: ...energy is in-in-in-insufficient. Must be repaired...

Sanchez: Hmph! Big Man Sanchez knew this would happen all along!
Clark: What's that, Sanchez?
Sanchez: I spent all my money on this, the newest model Rune landmine! If I move or loosen my grip, this thing'll explode!
Rune: Sanchez...?
Sophie: Sanchez! What are you going to do?
Sanchez: Come off it, clown! You've got eyes, don't you? What are you all waiting for? Get the hell out of here!
Lazer: Hmph, I've seen this trick a million times before...
Sanchez: Don't move or this is gonna blow! I'm not kidding you! I'll take you down with me!
Sanchez: I'm really gonna do it!!!
Lazer: ......
Sanchez: Quick!!! This baby's got a countdown timer!!
Sophie: ......Thank you, Sanchez.
Sophie: I'm sorry.
Rune: Ru-yi, let...go...
Ru-yi: No! Rune, stop strugg──
Rune: Sanchez...must...come...
Sophie: Let's go.
Rune: San...chez!!! SANCHEZ!!! Together!! We are...friends!!
Rune: SAN——
Lazer: ...Lesson learned. I didn't think you'd be so foolishly brave.
Lazer: Your friends have all left you. Now tell me, how does this story end? There's no way you'll catch up.
Sanchez: ...Your words...they're like......farts. Loud and stinky.
Lazer: Once you put down that landmine, I'm going to chop your hand off. That way you'll have nothing to threaten me with.
Lazer: Or perhaps you'd like to press it now. That way we'll be buried here together. What do you say?
Sanchez: ...hehehe...
Sanchez: ...General, your eye is indeed keen.
Sanchez: The landmine is fake...and I don't have the courage to blow myself up.
Lazer: ...With courage like that, I ought to let you go.
Lazer: ——Is that what you thought I'd say?
Lazer: People are selfish. Nobody sacrifices themselves for nothing.
Lazer: While you suffer in the flesh, you will see all the regrets that cower in your soul!
